336
00:22:31,083 --> 00:22:33,074
<i>They deserve a thank you,</i>

337
00:22:33,118 --> 00:22:36,087
<i>not another one
of your world-famous tantrums.</i>

338
00:22:36,121 --> 00:22:40,080
<i>Yeah, okay. I'd resign before
